headline: EAT raised, CAKE and DRI downgraded as Raymond James adjusts restaurant ratings
summary: Investing.com -- Raymond James has reshuffled its ratings across the restaurant sector, upgrading Brinker International while cutting its rating on Cheesecake Factory and Darden Restaurants.
